title: Rest In Peace, Personal Responsibility, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO55
description: Pay your respects to personal responsibility, who by all indications, appears to be dead in America.  In this episode of The MFCEO Project, Andy Frisella holds a funeral service for the thing that has built every great life, business, and even the U.S. of A.
